{"tid":1776610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請推 周梓樂同學追悼會將於本周四舉行","createTime":"2019-12-09T16:01:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T17:05:18.000Z","uid":204157,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3ccaa1dceca5e290927104f09aaa5d243150e19d","tid":1776610,"uid":204157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:01:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3PwhxuF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3PwhxuF.jpg&h=811e755c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《周同學追悼會》<br />\n<br />\n周家將於本周星期四舉辦追悼會，詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n日期：十二月十二日 (星期四)<br />\n時間：下午五時至八時<br />\n地點：大圍寶福紀念館<br />\n<br />\n校方將安排接駁巴士由科大往返場址，詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n科大上車時間：下午六時十五分<br />\n上車地點：中央廣場(Piazza)<br />\n紀念館上車時間：下午七時半<br />\n中途下車地點：大圍站及鑽石山站<br />\n<br />\n自行前往紀念館人士可於大圍站D、F或G出口選乘免費接駁巴士前往場址。<br />\n<br />\n若未能親身出席或有意捐獻者可存款到以下戶口：<br />\n<br />\n恆生銀行：361-008071-677<br />\n中國銀行：012-896-1-017333-7<br />\n東亞銀行：015-263-10-00009-1<br />\n<br />\n捐款將由校方代為收集，戶口將於十二月十六日(下周一)後停止接收。<br />\n<br />\n願周同學永遠安息，餘下之事交由我等完成。<br />\n<br />\n香港科技大學學生會<br />\n二零一九年十二月九日<br />\n<br />\n公眾人士可以出席。見到有手足推，想推埋一份。<br />\n原po: <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776496\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776496</a>"},{"pid":"e6d72ad149e75f131b6d1570f93c728fc7905db3","tid":1776610,"uid":204157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:02:11.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"9003b8d03fd74c8d804bb69105543204f49338b0","tid":1776610,"uid":204157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:02:23.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"2d71e46ae70e11c0fe5a40b5134d40bea865539b","tid":1776610,"uid":127553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmKV2z6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmKV2z6.jpg&h=241aee25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有班教育界痴線佬為左唔比學生落入聖誕節圈套<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776399</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b156bd275b1e880103b85857097bb0447ae59fad","tid":1776610,"uid":204157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:02:35.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"d156a18a205409af836522a75c7ecd65ab0f1e8c","tid":1776610,"uid":204157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:03:20.000Z","msg":"就快到聖誕啦 但係走咗嘅手足冇得同佢地屋企人一齊過囉"},{"pid":"8ac662877e318c53cb51468d3e6ac9c0fbc9938a","tid":1776610,"uid":204157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:03:36.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"cda22760fff999f6f4cf664bf0f9c111e57380df","tid":1776610,"uid":204157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:04:04.000Z","msg":"大家會去嘅！"},{"pid":"c5406e1faa181fc980be458722b86193b660f47c","tid":1776610,"uid":204157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:04:14.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"1a49935e37906aff67a5b96a7178f6568839af4d","tid":1776610,"uid":204157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:04:40.000Z","msg":"冇人幫推嘅"},{"pid":"4d06e98636b82475734cbdb41ba5f8b9aec5cfbd","tid":1776610,"uid":204157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:04:57.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"32e27a201ba2e6459c35ff47a134e10c0fc4c157","tid":1776610,"uid":204157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:05:13.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"77d187b1069705b3e520f39d1692314e9f57c68b","tid":1776610,"uid":204157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:05:28.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"33d82dd23ee3f3aad6ac01af51744282b11b6189","tid":1776610,"uid":204157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:05:42.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"c6d5593284d5b4d0f4875698f029986a2ba558c3","tid":1776610,"uid":204157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T16:05:58.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"443ceea057a733